channel.description:

First of all lets summarise what makes PWNscape very different from all the other servers out there:
1. We don't believe in downtime. 2. We have a tight and friendly community. 3. There is always a member of staff online to help. 4. We have unique features no other server has! 5. We actually update regularly.. 6. We focus on the small details! 7. We have an economy. 8. All our skills work perfectly!
